text:
Good portion for $4.50 fish& chips promotion.
Fish was fried nicely n not too dry, coleslaw is nicely seasoned. Will come back to try their other items on menu

Grilled chicken comes with mushroom sauce, we opt to have spaghetti to and it was also nice.  Not too mushy, slight spicy as it was oligo.
Chicken was cooked  nicely with rosemary and not too dry.

Stall is in the 3rd coffeeshop in Blk 22 Sin Ming Road. Food portion is adequate. Fries are tasty. Pasta is also done nicely. We ordered the 2 promotion items. Good deal. Adequate seating. Reasonable wait for food. Polite staff.

Delicious grilled marinated chicken covered in a rich, bold pepper sauce. I loved the chicken chop because the meat is always so flavorful and tender.

The service by Mr Imal is always excellent and cheerful.
Bought fish & chip and chicken chop for dinner. Food portion generous and food very tasty. Highly recommend! Having promo at $4.90 for the fish & chip & $5.90 for chicken shop now.
Very value for money chicken chop set with spaghetti $5.90 promotion. I like the whip potato flavour and coleslaw too.
